# Hi, I'm Ale Muñoz, Product Designer

I've spent two decades **building tools for the people who build things**.

[Design tools](https://sketch.com). [Development tools](https://zenrows.com). [Engineering Tools](https://qatium.com). [Productivity tools](https://bebanjo.com). I've built tools for myself, for my teams, and for the public. I've built communities, and I've built products. I've built things that have been used by millions of people, and things that have been used by just a handful of people.

I've worked at the intersection of design and technology for as long as I can remember. I'm comfortable with all steps of the product process and can do 0 to 1 product development, but my true passion is designing things and bringing them to life.

I also love orange, but can use other colors.

You can read more about [how I work](/how-i-work) or [check some of my recent projects](/projects).

I'm currently open to senior product design roles. Get in touch by [email](mailto:bomberstudios@gmail.com), on [Bluesky](https://bsky.app/profile/bomberstudios.com) or [LinkedIn](https://www.linkedin.com/in/bomberstudios/).
